reviews.review_text: Fine Matrix This is a very nice sounding matrix.  The Sugaree is really unique.

Hot 82 Show! One of best of the year? Certainly in the discussion.
When "Mexicali Blues" takes off, you know they band is playing HOT, and it certainly does achieve lift-off here. Incredible "Peggy-O", "Bird Song", great "Estimated" and "Stella" in the second set - this show has something for everyone! I also really like the "Iko" and "Man Smart" openings for Sets 1 and 2 - kind of like opening with the same tune, but not :) 

This Matrix sounds great and is the best I have heard of this show. Check it out!
Hot Damn! Thank you again Mr. Dusborn for another wonderful matrix.
